file.name: Schema_with_additional_properties.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: Market Data Exporter API
paths:
  /v4/endpoint:
    post:
      requestBody:
        content:
          'application/json':
            schema:
              type: array
              items:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/TypeQuery'
        required: true
      responses:
        '400':
          description: The request was ill-formed

components:
  schemas:
    TypeQuery:
      type: object
      properties:
        type:
          type: string
        filtered_keys:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/NaturalKey'
    NaturalKey:
      type: object
      additionalProperties:
        type: string
